::Sonata No. 1 for Solo Recorder ("The Bullfinch").<ref>{{harvnb|Hettrick|1971}}. "An arrow head pointing down over a note lowers it approximately a quarter step" {{harv|Tucker|1970|p=4}}.</ref>

